---
title: Grilled Mediterranean Salmon with Warm Creamy Orzo and Feta
description: This dinner brings the summer vibes! Orzo salad with spinach, tomatoes and tzatziki and spiced, grilled salmon pack big flavours inspired by the sunny Mediterranean coast!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-grille-a-la-mediterraneenne-e3b5052a.jpg
